727342f-a.title: Queens: Marathon Parkway - Van Zandt Avenue
727342f-a.text:
Marathon Parkway, below Van 2andt Avenue, Little Neck,
showing Frank Jackowski's place in the woods. Marathon Parkway
was forwerly Clinton Avende.
P. L. Sperr  June 10, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2,3
